snippet.title: Johnny DEPP v Amber HEARD Why Virginia by Lost Beyond Pluto Partial
snippet.description:
07.17.2020 

I don't really cover this types of videos. However, since I did the video about why "Meghan Is Not An 'A' List Actress" I felt like I should cover this. Also, Only because some of the women mentioned in this video stood for the TRUTH. The did not sit by and let it happened to an opposite sex.

I've included a partial video of "Lost Beyond Pluto" (YT Channel). She covers why Johnny Depp's case is being held in Virginia. Please go to her channel to see the rest of the video. The links to her YT channel and the video I highlighted are down below.
Check her channel out and subscribe to her channel. She knows what she's talking about.
